Package: rpubconnector
Type: Package
Title: Retrieve information from scopus.com and scholar.google.com
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bangyou Zheng
Maintainer: Bangyou Zheng <zheng.bangyou@gmail.com>
Description: 'TiddlyWiki' is a unique non-linear notebook for capturing, organising 
                 and sharing complex information. 'rpubconnector' retrieves information 
                 from 'Scopus' <https://www.scopus.com/> and 'Google Scholar' <https://scholar.google.com> 
                 into 'TiddlyWiki' <https://tiddlywiki.com>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://rpubconnector.bangyou.me/, https://github.com/byzheng/rpubconnector, https://byzheng.github.io/rpubconnector/
BugReports: https://github.com/byzheng/rpubconnector/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
  Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
   settings,
   purrr,
   dplyr,
   rlang,
   rscopus,
   rtiddlywiki,
   httr,
   stats,
   httr2,
   xml2
Remotes:
    byzheng/rtiddlywiki,
    muschellij2/rscopus
